Date: Wed, 17 Jan 2018 21:21:48 +0200
Subject: drm/i915: Nuke intel_dp->channel_eq_status
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit
Git-commit: 2fed7955bf4c2e87e8b3759939fd0ad961da776e
Patch-mainline: v4.17-rc1
References: FATE#326289 FATE#326079 FATE#326049 FATE#322398 FATE#326166

intel_dp->channel_eq_status is used in exactly one function, and we
don't need it to persist between calls. So just go back to using a
local variable instead.

